Job Description
Share
Mechanical Engineers with Oil & Gas industry experienced candidates are required for a
Leading Oil & Gas Group Co. in Abudhabi, UAE -
Attractive Salary + 42 days p.a., Family Accommodation @ AED 2,25,000 plus furniture purchase allowance, Education Assistance, Insurance, Free Medical, End of Service Benefit, etc
Job Purpose :
As MECHANICAL ENGINEER - To
SUPERVISE MECH. ENGG. AND DESIGN FOR STATIONARY EQUIPMENT / PACKAGES AND DEVELOPMENT FOR
CIVIL/BUILDINGS CONSTRUCTION PROJECTS - OFFSHORE-OIL&GAS;
PRODUCTION / TREATMENT / REFINING / TRANSPORTATION AND PETROCHEMICAL PROJECTS / NEW PROJECTS, HANDLE INTEGRITY ISSUES RELATED TO INFRA & UTILITIES.
Desired Candidate Profile
Bachelors Degree in Mechanical Engineering or equivalent with min. 15 years of experience - more than 6 years exp. in Oil & Gas Industry-Offshore Design & detailed engineering and Gulf Exp. is essential.
Must be familiar with -DESIGN-DETAILED ENGINEERING - OFFSHORE-OIL&GAS-CONSTRUCTION; PROJECTS-PIPING-DESIGN CODES-PDMS-AUTOCAD-SOUR SERVICES-BROWNFIELD PROJECTS-FFS ANALYSIS-CAESAR II-INTERNATIONAL EPC CONTRACTORS SPECIFICATIONS
